  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マナが……
世界中のマナが
消えていく……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Th-the Mana....all of the Mana in the world...it's 
disappearing... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうして！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>WHY!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうして、発射させたの！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>WHY DID YOU HAVE TO FIRE IT!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あのまま、放っておけば、
わが国は滅びていた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I didn't do this our country would have been ruined. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282016</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その代償が……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's just an excuse...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……私だって同罪よね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...And...I'm just as guilty as you are...For building this 
monstrosity... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……メルティアが
悪いわけじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;tia, you aren't evil. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦争がすべて悪い。
オレたちをこんなふうにした
この戦争が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>War is full of hatred. Thanks to this stupid war my 
parents... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もし、あなたが
奴らに両親を
殺されてなければ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see. Yeah they killed your parents, didn't they...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もし、おまえがもっと
両親に愛情を
もらっていれば</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And thanks to the war you have been discarded by your 
parents... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>くっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guh... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>メルティア……！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;tia...!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うっ……くっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh...guh... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マナが……
薄くなってきてるのよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Mana...it's disappearing completely... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……おしまいよ、この星は、
デリス・カーラーンは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...This is the end of our world. This is how Derris Kharlan 
dies... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お父様が願われていた
デリス・カーラーンの
平和は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We couldn't fulfill father's promise...for a peaceful 
Derris Kharlan... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふっ……
デリス・カーラーンの
平和、か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heh...Peace for...Derris Kharlan...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287236</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたがたは……
罰を受けなければなりません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You two...There is no fitting punishment for the 
transgressions you committed... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287236</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>星を滅ぼした大罪に
報いるための罰を</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You have extinguished the life of a whole planet. Snatched 
away the future of millions. For such a sin your punishment... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_020</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレたちは……悪くない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No...we didn't mean...bad... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_021</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全部、戦争のせい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's all...the war's fault... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287812</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当に……
そうでしょうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So...you believe that? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_023</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……わかりました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Understood. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_024</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたがたに
機会を与えましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I shall give you one last chance. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_025</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私はあなたがたを子どもに戻し、
異なる時、異なる場所へ
飛ばします</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You will live again. In a different place. In a different 
time. Where no conflict will taint your judgment. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_026</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……そして試練を受けなさい。
そこで私は見定めましょう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...And then you will be tested. I shall make sure proper 
judgment is passed. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>287988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_300_060_027</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたがたの本質が
善なのか悪なのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Judgment whether your essence is evil or good. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>5</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
